<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 页面未找到 - Affirm后台管理</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center; padding: 80px 20px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 6rem; margin: 0; color: #e74c3c;">404</h1>
        <h2>页面未找到</h2>
        <p>请求的路径 <code><%= url %></code> 不存在。</p>
        <a href="/admin" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:20px; padding:10px 24px; background:#3498db; color:#fff; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none;">返回仪表板</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
